  "conclusion": "Data conclusively demonstrates systematic, unauthorized, and highly toxic chemical discharge from the NorthStar Chemical Solutions Riverbend Plant into the protected Silver River watershed. Contaminant levels consistently exceed federal safety limits by several hundredfold, indicating deliberate bypass of wastewater treatment systems. Immediate enforcement action is recommended."
